entries.source: Chat Edit: 'I don't want to do task 2 anymore. Do only task 1 for me, and also add "previous" button too, not just "next" button. Note that this feature should only work on the local app, don't touch the server'

Chat Edit: 'There are issues:
- The next, previous button on light theme mode are indistinguishable
- There were still "File is not a Windows PE executable" result page with no next/previous button showing then disappeared. The non-PE files later showed as benign, along with other PE files, with proper buttons. I want the "File is not a Windows PE executable" result page to be kept, with proper buttons.'

Chat Edit: '- The "next" button style was correctly fixed, but the "previous" button was not. 
And I want to move the buttons to the top of the page, not their current positions now.'
Chat Edit: 'My QR idea change to QR containing the json report of that specific file, show the QR on each file's scan result's page'
Chat Edit: 'I want to add a QR for each file's result (only do for PE file), show the QR on the result page. The QR contains its json report'
Chat Edit: 'I want to add new feature: A "home" button to return to the inital page of the local app when clicking on it. Do it such that it's most clean and efficienct'
